_ASSETS 业务真源","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":35,"content":"  E2 playbackClipId / play_system_prompt.clipId / assetRefs 接真源","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":36,"content":"  E3 头像直传（可与 E1 共用上传基础设施）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":37,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":38,"content":"阶段 F · 包级元数据与 Schedule 约定（P1）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":39,"content":"  F1 assetRefs / worldFacts / meta.imports|exports 最小可编（表单或受控 JSON 块二选一）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":40,"content":"  F2 Schedule 卡落盘分工：故事包内 schedule vs characters/schedule-cards","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":41,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":42,"content":"阶段 G · UX 债 + 校验定位 + 收口","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":43,"content":"  G1 删遗留角色 + golden_handoff/demo-user 迁移；变体 id；时段 Select；包列表搜索+新建","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":44,"content":"  G2 保存前 validatePackage + error 路径定位（package/card/exit）；阻断写盘","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":45,"content":"  G3 docs/AI 同步 + 全批验收勾选","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":54,"content":"| 调试器 **真会话**（beginCall 驱动） | 可选尾任务仅读盘展示 validate，不 Host |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":55,"content":"| 导入导出正式 ZIP 管道 | 列表导入保持现状 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"| 第二幕内容包 | 不扩叙事 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":57,"content":"| 单卡增量 API | 仍整包保存 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":58,"content":"| ExitCondition **完整** and/or/not 嵌套树 UI | v1 仅常用叶子 + always；复杂嵌套另批或 JSON 逃生 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":59,"content":"| Free 卡主编辑入口迁到故事编辑器 | Free 卡真源仍在 `characters/free-cards/` + 角色库 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":61,"content":"### 1.3 与前置里程碑的关系","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":62,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"| 前置 | 关系 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":64,"content":"|------|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":65,"content":"| 第三步 | 读写盘已通；本批修 participants 误用、conf.cards 不同步、condition 假字段 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":66,"content":"| 细化修改 7 | Effect 15 种面板已通；本批补 critical roundtrip、资产 id 真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"| docs/AI 07 | 资源库/条件 DSL/新建包等纳入本批 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":68,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":69,"content":"**刀序铁律：** A → B → C → D → E → F → G。**禁止**跳步（例：未改 validate 就先全库锚点双轨；未 E1 就宣称 ASSET 校验可编）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":70,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":86,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":87,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":88,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":89,"content":"| 角色真源 | **仅** `data/characters/<agentId>.json` + `/api/characters` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":90,"content":"| 故事包不私有角色 | **禁止** `participants` 当白名单；作者不手维护 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":91,"content":"| 「本包用到谁」 | `cards[].ownerAgentId` + effects 内 `agentId` + attach 目标归属 **派生** |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":92,"content":"| 编辑器锚点 | **全库**显示；挂卡数来自本包 cards；未用可灰显 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":93,"content":"| 「添加角色」 | **仅**角色库新建；不是加入包 participants |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":94,"content":"| participants | 新包可不写；保存推荐不写；校验现场派生 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":95,"content":"| layout.lanes | Studio 按库序或「有卡者优先」派生；引擎忽略 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":97,"content":"### 2.1 引擎 validatePackage 改造","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":100,"content":"2. **`REFERENCED_AGENT_UNKNOWN`**（error）：派生 id 不在角色库。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":101,"content":"3. **`validateParticipantsCharacters`** 对**派生集合**执行。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":102,"content":"4. **`PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN`**：非空遗留 participants 未知 → **warning**「遗留字段将忽略」；空数组不报错。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":103,"content":"5. **ownerAgentId 不在旧 participants** 但在角色库 → 不得 error。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":104,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":105,"content":"### 2.2 包内卡生命周期（P0）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":106,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":107,"content":"| 操作 | 必须行为 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":108,"content":"|------|----------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":109,"content":"| 底栏放置新 CallCard | 生成 cardId；追加 `conf.cards[]`；新建 `cards/<cardId>.s-card.json`；画布节点与 conf 一致 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":110,"content":"| 画布删除 CallCard | 从 `conf.cards[]` 移除；**删除**对应 s-card 文件（若 entryCardId 指向该卡则阻止或强制改入口） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":111,"content":"| 保存整包 | `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 **conf.cards 与磁盘卡文件并集**（以画布为准），禁止只改 layout 不改 conf |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":112,"content":"| orphan 磁盘卡 | 未在 conf 索引的 s-card → validate `CARD_FILE_ORPHAN` warning；保存时可清理或保留策略写清 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":113,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":114,"content":"**禁止：** 仅会话内新增节点，保存后 conf 仍只有打开时的卡列表。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":115,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":116,"content":"### 2.3 entryCardId 与 effect.critical","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":162,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":163,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":164,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":165,"content":"| assetRefs | 包配置可编；与全局 assets 下拉联动 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":166,"content":"| worldFacts / meta | 最小表单或受控 JSON 块（实现二选一）；不要求可视化编辑器 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":167,"content":"| Schedule 卡 | **钉死分工**（写入需求 01/19）：故事包内 `cardKind=schedule` 仅剧情调度节点；角色日常 `schedule-cards/` 由角色库/专用路径维护；Studio 创建 schedule 卡时落盘路径与 `schedule_recurring_call` 校验一致 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":168,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":169,"content":"### 2.8 故事包列表与新建","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":170,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":171,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":172,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":233,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":234,"content":"- [ ] participants 可选；collectReferencedAgentIds 单测覆盖 effects 内 agentId","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":235,"content":"- [ ] wrong_number_act1、golden_handoff（迁移后）validate 无 error","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":236,"content":"- [ ] `npm run quality:engine` 全绿","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":237,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":238,"content":"### 包内卡生命周期","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":239,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":240,"content":"- [ ] 底栏新建卡 → conf.cards + s-card 文件存在；刷新仍在","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":241,"content":"- [ ] 删卡 → conf 与磁盘文件同步移除","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":242,"content":"- [ ] entryCardId 可改且 validate 通过","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":243,"content":"- [ ] effect.critical 保存 roundtrip 不丢","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":244,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":245,"content":"### 出口条件","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":279,"content":"## 6. 给批执行 Agent 的硬停语境","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":280,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":281,"content":"命中以下应 `BLOCKED`：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":282,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":283,"content":"- 锚点仍仅 conf.participants 子集 / 双轨白名单","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":284,"content":"- 新建卡不写 conf.cards 或不建 s-card.json","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":285,"content":"- 删卡不删磁盘或 conf 不同步","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":286,"content":"- conditionSummary 写盘替代 exit.condition 或保存一律 DEFAULT_CONDITION","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":287,"content":"- critical 保存丢失","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":288,"content":"- MOCK_ASSETS 仍作资源业务真源","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":289,"content":"- validate 失败仍 PUT","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":129,"totalMatchedLines":17,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-3b5e78c5-28d3-41c4-9212-22ba981ff20b-3\nfc_2ecc4f5e-3a8f-9a7a-98a6-d3614888685d_2","startedAtMs":"1784716848411","completedAtMs":"1784716848608"},"model_call_id":"f579b868-20d4-41a5-bec6-09dac4fc1899-1-x9f6","session_id":"1584d004-bd1e-41ee-8306-5e5bd087a012","timestamp_ms":1784716848610}
