{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-b1ea79aa-e485-4cdf-8ef7-a1de4b41af9b-5\nfc_407ca518-16a1-9750-bc5f-f222f0f442e4_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","offset":105,"limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"### 2.2 包内卡生命周期（P0）\n\n| 操作 | 必须行为 |\n|------|----------|\n| 底栏放置新 CallCard | 生成 cardId；追加 `conf.cards[]`；新建 `cards/<cardId>.s-card.json`；画布节点与 conf 一致 |\n| 画布删除 CallCard | 从 `conf.cards[]` 移除；**删除**对应 s-card 文件（若 entryCardId 指向该卡则阻止或强制改入口） |\n| 保存整包 | `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 **conf.cards 与磁盘卡文件并集**（以画布为准），禁止只改 layout 不改 conf |\n| orphan 磁盘卡 | 未在 conf 索引的 s-card → validate `CARD_FILE_ORPHAN` warning；保存时可清理或保留策略写清 |\n\n**禁止：** 仅会话内新增节点，保存后 conf 仍只有打开时的卡列表。\n\n### 2.3 entryCardId 与 effect.critical\n\n| 项 | 口径 |\n|----|------|\n| entryCardId | 包配置或章节浮窗可 Select 本包 cardId；新建包默认指向首张 story 卡或占位 |\n| critical | 读盘保留；投影不丢；Effect 面板 boolean「失败则中止后续」；写回 effect.critical |\n\n### 2.4 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1（P0）\n\n**问题：** 现 `conditionSummary` 仅 UI 人话；写盘用 `base.condition ?? DEFAULT_CONDITION`，改 summary **不改**引擎 condition。\n\n**v1 必须：**\n\n| op | 面板 |\n|----|------|\n| `always` | 单选「始终」 |\n| `outcome_flag` | flag Select（对齐 OutcomeFlagSchema）+ equals 布尔 |\n| `beat_completed` | beatId Select（来自本卡 objectives.requiredBeats + 手填逃生） |\n| `beat_missing` | 同上 |","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":294,"fileSize":12906,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","readRange":{"startLine":105,"endLine":134},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-b1ea79aa-e485-4cdf-8ef7-a1de4b41af9b-5\nfc_407ca518-16a1-9750-bc5f-f222f0f442e4_0","startedAtMs":"1784716852827","completedAtMs":"1784716853034"},"model_call_id":"f579b868-20d4-41a5-bec6-09dac4fc1899-2-p24n","session_id":"1584d004-bd1e-41ee-8306-5e5bd087a012","timestamp_ms":1784716853019}
